728595f-a.title: Richmond: Bement Avenue - Henderson Avenue
728595f-a.text:
163 Bement Ave., north of the N.E. corner of Henderson Ave.,
showing the Gratacap house. The house is about 100 feet back of
the Avenue.
July 7, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
